name: Electronic Accessory Bag
description:
Computer bags can be so boring, but they definitely protect your laptop.  Why not add a little pep and color to your laptop bag and keep your accessories organized?

This bag has plush, sturdy interfacing to protect your items and is a workhorse bag in that it has two 5" by 6" pockets as well as a 10" by 10" zippered pocket.  Even when it is full as pictured below, you could still slip a compact netbook, ipad, nook, or kindle inside.

Spot clean recommended.

Measurements:
12 1/2" tall 
10" across

interior
1- 10 x 10 zippered pocket that matches the decorative stripe
2- 5 x 6 padded pockets

name: Tree Wristlet with Decorative Stripe
description:
This wristlet is bursting with color and is ready to be filled with your cell, lip balm, keys, and any other accessories you may need.  Perfect for garage sale-ing or shopping at the mall, this wristlet keeps all your necessities in one place and the nifty strap keeps it close!  Lined with the same fabric as the decorative stripe this wristlet is sure to put a smile on your face.  I love the contrast of the green treetops and the purple background.

Spot clean recommended.

Measurements:
6 1/4" by 5 1/4"
8 " Strap

name: Goody Bag Purple/Green Foliage with Decorative Stripe
description:
The bright greens and purples in this fabric are sure to make you smile!  This goody bag is perfect for your accessories whether you are going on a day trip or an overnight.  Lined with the same fabric as the decorative stripe this goody bag is fashionable both inside and out and its boxed corners allow it to stand upright for easy access.

Spot clean recommended.

Measurements:
7" tall
10" long
2 1/2" wide at base
7" strap
